Cole Sprouse https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cole_Sprouse 0 Cole Mitchell Sprouse (born August 4, 1992) is an American actor, and twin brother of Dylan Sprouse. He is known for his role as Cody Martin on the Disney Channel series The Suite Life of Zack Cody and its spinoff The Suite Life on Deck. As of 2017, Sprouse stars as Jughead Jones on The CW television series Riverdale. Cole_Mitchell_Sprouse ( born August_4_,_1992 ) is an_American_actor , and twin_brother of Dylan_Sprouse .
